He Was A Fireman He Never Got To The Fire
In Time So He Trained To Be Faster And Stronger.

He Always Wanted To Be A Black Enemy
So Everyday He Spent 2 Hours In A Pitch Black
Room And His Dream Came True.
The Snappy Snache That Hides In Dark Places.

Shadows Combined Together With Dark Matter
And Hippoe Cells And Made This Beast.

Been In So Many Fights His Bones Are Exposed
Dont Underestimate Him Though He Packs Quite A Punch.

Show those enemies your iron will
with Iron Cat!, Those enemies will
Regret playing around with Iron Cat ðŸ˜ˆ
